</title>
<subSubSection id="73228112D66DD326DC806C3A6ADF7FDF" pageId="null" pageNumber="824" type="description">
<paragraph id="96EC3BAFF7044577A5511861049EDA25" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
Ausdauernd, locker- bis dichtrasig; 5-15 cm hoch. Stengel am Grund niederliegend, mit aufsteigenden 
<normalizedToken id="0F9212091564B0E0DBDA7FA844354EE0" originalValue="Ästen" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Aesten</normalizedToken>
, kurz abstehend und 
<normalizedToken id="E0B566107DB08685A7C52DB78A363EC9" originalValue="drüsig" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">druesig</normalizedToken>
, oft 2zeilig behaart (Haare 0,1-0,2 mm lang). 
<emphasis id="B116E37F6A45FC711643B0A63F337A86" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<normalizedToken id="CDB39E72B29EE6DC1132F93EA7E175B7" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
schmal lanzettlich, mit 0,5-0,8 mm langer, grannenartiger Spitze, 0,5-1,2 cm lang, 5-20mal so lang wie breit
</emphasis>
, vortretend 3nervig (davon 2 Nerven 
<normalizedToken id="D2693E11F1A6E0F3CB46D451D3787C42" originalValue="randständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">randstaendig</normalizedToken>
), am Grunde bewimpert, sonst kahl. 
<emphasis id="E2E974E2A17604AC10C0F6D9C7FE6E6D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Fruchtstiele 3-5mal so lang wie der Kelch.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="1242DAA4AFC02D3B9379CD00294EC898" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
1-3nervig, 3,5-6 mm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="725615DF7B50C43498567A3198E8C3A9" originalValue="drüsig" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">druesig</normalizedToken>
behaart. 
<normalizedToken id="47F125860071657D635B3ECBF6012B84" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="0B68854B37213A865EFBC631764F2112" originalValue="1½-2½" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">11/2-21/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="30E8D9834B52C9794267B635497E5DB4" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="2EE4C9CD64BC195569DE37261A64B633" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">weiss</normalizedToken>
. Kapsel 
<normalizedToken id="DC42B3CA28E278252B5B12004A488B7A" originalValue="1¼-1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">11/4-11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="0B42E991FF64E4C43116707E33DD8FB1" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="393441C665BE19E2CAB2411C1CC7C689" originalValue="eiförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">eifoermig</normalizedToken>
. Samen 1,2-1,5 mm lang, mit 
<normalizedToken id="467BD96B4CF77C3AB518BF31BDC6EFCA" originalValue="körniger" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">koerniger</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="6D7709D490FCBA2E1051A5C572E39B74" originalValue="Oberfläche" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Oberflaeche</normalizedToken>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="1A4CBF6216A5BF3719DF21C8362FFF10" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="D8A78FDD028AB9E0C96CAEBB80FC43ED" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="47EF299EC84357359CC8A70D10A16E73" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="E992F6D786A902E6B79977A255282ECE" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A8461AB6432FEF82FA23145C0177E388" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<emphasis id="2A8040261B7CE684DA1C818ACDD8D6E6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="5D780C6971C764259774049CFEFC4816" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">44:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Jura (Chasseron) und aus Spanien (Favarger 1959).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="296A69E26DAB4F1BDE68D490ACC02183" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<emphasis id="EB0749B2E874B0C80771F0D5156955E2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan, subalpin und alpin. Steinige 
<normalizedToken id="2129ED0801162E74ECCC1BB3831CBDC6" originalValue="Kalkböden" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kalkboeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Felsen, 
<normalizedToken id="B955414B214CA8A0BCABD3706AB1F7CD" originalValue="Geröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Geroell</normalizedToken>
, steinige Wiesen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="88955C80329E518A465C8BBC74463DBD" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<emphasis id="C9A4B1881F42C062FFEB57190F1C5922" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="EC9C261A800A02E0690CA6560BA2E238" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="9F7ECEA285F3732E7F4FC24577C5BC3A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">westlich</emphasis>
): Kleiner Atlas, Gebirge der Iberischen Halbinsel, 
<normalizedToken id="BA4DB65DC2EF2452AEFD2A46A2DD526B" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="A49FC45B72FD0B900B0B105CBFDB715A" originalValue="südfranzösische" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedfranzoesische</normalizedToken>
Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="DDD180464BBCA9739E02C1C8157EB850" originalValue="südliche" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedliche</normalizedToken>
Alpen, 
<normalizedToken id="8C48340EA5F3D97454E5E9860DC386D7" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura, Apennin, 
<normalizedToken id="5B61A9E509D39B685C50400BBECFFACE" originalValue="Mähren" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Maehren</normalizedToken>
. - Im Gebiet: Alpen von Savoyen, 
<normalizedToken id="7B0D901FC3DD1E2BC76C6A21B9060B7F" originalValue="südlicher" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedlicher</normalizedToken>
Jura (Fort de 
<normalizedToken id="47285EE42DB50F47FF717ED9FF150EA1" originalValue="l’Ecluse" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">l'Ecluse</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="F81275D1C351376BC9D6EAD20E16FC46" originalValue="Salève" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Saleve</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="C11C09EAF246B804AA5B2D5EC522970E" originalValue="Dôle" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Dole</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="ECC0667ECE22D257059A3A42CCE93637" originalValue="Vallée" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Vallee</normalizedToken>
de Joux, Suchet, Aiguilles de Baulmes, Chasseron).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
